latestIgtvVideos.title: Which is your favourite look ? 1.2.3.4- Tube top styled in four easy ways '
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have styled my lavender gatherer tube top in four very easy ways using the options already available in wardrobe to give a twist to regular wear .

Look 1 - 
Monotone - color on color look with shorts . You can simply accessorise this look as per the event .

Look 2 - Color blocking over a dress - don't forget the accessories 

Look 3 - With a denim jacket and denim skirt - is my favourite look , tube tops are best done with jackets or blazers and i have paired entire denim look to add that chic factor 

Look 4 - Over a white shirt and i am a fan of monotone looks so i have kept white on white as i am already breaking the monotony with lavender on it 

You can create this look with any shirt you have !
Experiment different colors as per your choice 💜

And yes have done this styling video in little different style using my favourite track by 
@nehakakkar 🌻❤️
